snippet: Keith Allen's documentary, "Unlawful Killing," suggests that a conspiracy of British royalty, politicians and secret service officers was to blame for the deaths of Princess Diana and Dodi al-Fayed.
abstract: Keith Allen's documentary, "Unlawful Killing," suggests that a conspiracy of British royalty, politicians and secret service officers was to blame for the deaths of Princess Diana and Dodi al-Fayed.

headline.main: Controversial Documentary on Death of Princess Diana Is Shelved
